## TypeScript Configuration

### Header Config
- Interface: HeaderConfig
- Properties:
  - logoText: string
  - logoIcon: string
  - navItems: Array<{text: string, href: string, isActive?: boolean}>
  - heroContent?: {title: string, subtitle: string, ctaText: string, ctaHref: string}
  - heroClass?: string
- Customization: Update initHeader() function for page-specific configurations

### Footer Config
- Interface: FooterConfig
- Properties:
  - location: {title: string, address: string[], directionsLink: string}
  - contact: {title: string, description: string, phone: string, email: string, socialMedia: Array<{platform: string, url: string, icon: string}>}
  - copyright: string
- Customization: Update initFooter() function for page-specific configurations

### Global Objects
#### Header
- Name: window.termopilasHeader
- Methods:
  - updateConfig(config): Updates header with provided configuration
  - regenerateHeader(): Regenerates header with default configuration

#### Footer
- Name: window.termopilasFooter
- Methods:
  - updateConfig(config): Updates footer with provided configuration
  - regenerateFooter(): Regenerates footer with default configuration

